In this video interview, Africa analyst at Rand Merchant Bank (RMB) Neville Mandimika answers the following questions:1. What is the methodology behind RMB s Where to Invest in Africa A Guide to Corporate Investment report? 2. Take us through the findings of the report? 3. In which sectors are we seeing large investments coming through? 4. How have rankings changed over the years? E.g. in 2013, Nigeria became the second most attractive investment destination in Africa. 5. Which are some of the countries that are bubbling under and have strong potential?This video was sponsored by RMB.